{{Infobox dungeon |name = Malie Garden |image = [[File:Malie Garden.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Malie Garden. |tokens = 975,000 |location = North of Malie City. }}
'''Malie Garden''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Alola]]. It initially has 121 tiles arranged in a 11x11 square, including 11 chest tiles, 41 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 13,483,476 HP.
